<br/>
		RE: Account Number Ending in  {!RIGHT((Product__c.Name), 4)}
		<br><br>
		Outstanding Balance <strong> {!Product__c.Current_Balance__c}</strong> 
		<br><br>
		 <h2 style="text-align: center;"><b><u>                
                FINAL NOTICE                
                </b></u> </h2>
		<br/><br/>
        Dear {!Product__c.First_Name__c},<br><br>

<span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm MasterCard", 'initial;', 'none;')}" >
According to our records, you have failed to make payment on your Affirm Mastercard® for the above mentioned outstanding debt. Due to not complying with the previous payment requests, we are now considering assigning your account to a collection agency and/or legal action to recover the above amount
                                 
                                 </span>
                                 <span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm Term Loan", 'initial;', 'none;')}" >
                                 
                                According to our records, you have failed to make payment on your Affirm Term Loan for the above mentioned outstanding debt. Due to not complying with the previous payment requests, we are now considering assigning your account to a collection agency and/or legal action to recover the above amount.

                                 </span>







		
		<br/><br/>
		Immediate payment is now required – contact us immediately at <strong>1-855-266-3131</strong> to make your payment arrangement.
		<br/><br/>
		Failure to make payment will further negatively impact your credit rating with the possibility of being denied future credit.
		<br/><br/><br/>
		<span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm MasterCard", 'initial;', 'none;')}" ><strong>
        Alternatively, you can make your payment using the convenient options listed below:
        </strong>
                                 
                                 </span>
                                 <span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm Term Loan", 'initial;', 'none;')}" >
                                 <strong>
                                Choose one of our convenient payment options listed below: </strong>

                                 </span>
		
		<br>
		<table style="padding-left:10px;margin-top:4px">
