				</td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td class="tdText"><span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm MasterCard", 'initial;', 'none;')}" >
                                 Set up a one-time bill payment through your online banking. Just add Payee: “Affirm Mastercard” or pay directly at your local bank.
                                 </span>
                                 <span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm Term Loan", 'initial;', 'none;')}" >
                                Set up a onetime bill payment through your online banking if you bank with BMO, TD, BNS, Credit Unions or Tangerine. Just add Payee: “Affrim Financial”. Account number 000{!Product__c.Name} Or pay directly at your local bank.
                                 </span></td>
			</tr>
			<tr><tr>
				<td class="imageClass"> <img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmPC&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/>
				</td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
                                <td class="tdText">
				<span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm MasterCard", 'initial;', 'none;')}" >
                                 Visit a Western Union with a Western Union Quick Collect (WUQC). Use “Affirm Canada” for code city, “BC” for code Province.
                                 </span>
                                 <span style="display: {!IF(Product__c.Product_Type_Display_Name__c == "Affirm Term Loan", 'initial;', 'none;')}" >
